DESCR
  N. Artrith and A. Urban, Comput. Mater. Sci. 114 (2016) 135-150.
  N. Artrith, A. Urban, and G. Ceder, Phys. Rev. B 96 (2017) 014112.
END DESCR

ATOM Fe #central atom

ENV 2 # A list of all atomic species that may occur in the environment of the central atom and are captured by this setup. No blank lines are allowed.
Fe
S

RMIN 0.75d0 #the minimum distance between each atom

# The following example uses a Chebyshev basis set with a cutoff of 8.0 Å for the radial expansion (expansion order 16)
# and a cutoff of 6.5 Å for the angular expansion (expansion order 4).
BASIS type=Chebyshev
radial_Rc = 8.0  radial_N = 16 angular_Rc = 6.5  angular_N = 4
